com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class CompositeLayoutData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.LayoutData
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.CompositeLayoutData

  • public class CompositeLayoutData
extends LayoutData
    Combines several LayoutData instances.

    This is especially useful if several layouts are run at once, for example a general layout and a subsequent edge routing.
